      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped cherry tomatoes</strong> to a bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and the<strong> chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Stir it all together – this is your <strong>tomato salsa</strong></p>",
