      "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>sweet potato </strong>is tender, divide them between the <strong>tortillas</strong>, covering only half, and crush down gently with the back of a spoon (this will help the tortillas stick together)</p><p>Crumble your <strong>Greek cheese </strong>over the<strong> </strong>crushed<strong> </strong>sweet<strong> </strong>potato<strong> </strong>and add the<strong> sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Roll the <strong>tortillas</strong> tightly to form a cigar shape – these are your<strong> sweet potato & Greek cheese</strong> <strong>taquitos</strong></p>",
