    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, mix the <strong>mayo</strong> and <strong>chipotle paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>and a grind of <strong>pepper </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>chipotle mayo</strong></p>",
