      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>sweet potato & Greek cheese taquitos</strong> over the <strong>baby leaf salad </strong>and<strong> tomato salsa</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the<strong> chipotle mayo</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
